Q1.   Suppose You have a Travel Website landing page.centre its title and subtitle togeter,apply proper CSS.
Ans.    <!DOCTYPE html>
        <html lang="en">
            <head>
                <link rel="stylesheet" href="./A3.1.css">
                <title>Travel-Website</title>
            </head>
            <body>
                <div class="one">

                    <h2>Welcome In Indian-Airlines</h2>
                    <p class="subtitle">~Your Comfort is Our Priority~</p>
                </div>
            </body>
        </html>
               
Q2.  Refering the above question,apply proper background CSS properties to the page.(Avoid scroll,we need only landing page).
Ans.     *{
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        body{
            background-color: blueviolet;
        }
        h2{
            margin: 0 auto;


            width: 500px;

            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: crimson;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif ;
            letter-spacing:2px;

        }
        .subtitle{
           margin: 0 auto;
            width: 250px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            font-style:italic;
          }
          
